### Security Documentation
- Must document potential security considerations
- Must document attack vectors
- Must include warnings about common pitfalls
- Must provide security recommendations for production use

### Best Practices
- Must follow Noir's security best practices
- Must document known limitations
- Must document edge cases
- Must include security testing procedures
